# Odoo Manufacturing Analytics Platform

A modern manufacturing management and analytics dashboard built with React, Vite, TypeScript, and shadcn/ui. This project provides a full-featured frontend for managing manufacturing orders, BOMs, work orders, inventory, and advanced analytics, using static demo data for all modules except authentication.

## üöÄ Features

- **Authentication**: Secure login/register with role-based access
- **Dashboard**: KPIs, order status, and quick insights
- **Manufacturing Orders**: View, filter, and create orders 
- **BOM Management**: Bill of Materials explorer 
- **Work Orders & Centers**: Track operations and resources 
- **Stock Ledger**: Inventory and material tracking 
- **Reports & Analytics**: Interactive charts, trends, and cost analysis
- **Responsive UI**: Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile
- **Modern Stack**: React 18, Vite, TypeScript, shadcn/ui, Recharts

## üõ†Ô∏è Getting Started

1. **Install dependencies**
	 ```bash
	 cd frontend
	 npm install
	 ```

2. **Run the development server**
	 ```bash
	 npm run dev
	 ```
	 Open [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080) in your browser.

3. **Authentication**
	 - Only the login/register/forgot password pages use dynamic data.
	 - All other pages use static demo data for instant loading and demo purposes.

## üì¶ Project Structure

```
frontend/
	src/
		components/
			dashboard/
			manufacturing-orders/
			bom/
			work-orders/
			work-centers/
			stock-ledger/
			reports/
			ui/
		
		pages/
			Index.tsx          # Main app shell and routing
		context/
			AuthContext.tsx    # Authentication context
		services/
			apiClient.js       # API client (used only for auth)
```

## üìä Analytics & Reporting

- Interactive charts powered by [Recharts](https://recharts.org/)
- KPIs: Orders, revenue, efficiency, quality, costs, resource utilization
- All analytics use realistic static data for demo and development

## üñåÔ∏è UI/UX

- Built with MUI for beautiful, accessible components
- Sidebar navigation for all modules
- Tabbed analytics dashboard
- Color-coded metrics and responsive layouts

